tika.dc.description: If you have diabetes and absolutely love those wonderful comfort foods of The South, you've come to the right place. Just imagine being able to eat all your favorite foods while still adhering to your diabetic food plan!If you love, love, love Paula Deen like I do, you're gonna love this cookbook! I guarantee it! Paula Deen is beautiful, she's fabulous, she's amazing, she's an American success story, she's The South personified, she's one of the best chefs on the planet, she's a STAR and she's a diabetic! Finally, a cookbook for the diabetic foodie!Here's A Preview Of The Fabulous Diabetic Recipes You'll Find In The Paula Deen Would LOVE These Diabetic Southern Comfort Foods Recipes CookbookPaula Deen Would Love This Diabetic Apple Pie Recipe!Paula Deen Would Love This Diabetic Baked Beans Recipe!Paula Deen Would Love This Diabetic Banana Pudding Recipe!Paula Deen Would Love This Diabetic Bean and Bacon Soup Recipe!Paula Deen Would Love This Diabetic Beef Gravy Recipe!Paula Deen...
